name: Top5s
profile:
Welcome to Top5s. We cover some of the most interesting subjects in the world! From History & Facts to Paranormal & Mysteries. It started out with list type videos, which are still uploaded every Saturday, but we now also produce Series & Documentaries every few weeks. Not to mention the most exciting month of the year…OCTOBER! Every year on this month we roll out numerous videos packed full of haunting content, so look no further for your horror fix!

We’ve developed a significant following over the years of like-minded people who love to discover, explore & discuss the secrets of our planet… making Top5s comment sections an exciting place to share your thoughts. But if you would like to share further, take a look at the Top5s website - home of an array of exclusive articles & a place to share your own supernatural stories, which may even be featured in a Top5s video!

Now you’ve had the rundown, it’s time to ‘Sit back, Relax, & Enjoy the Videos!
